20top%20three%20factors%20and%20how%20HPS%20met%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a516f81a-f515-41fb-8ca3-1e87ed209f75%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECultural%20fit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%2C%20an%2018-year%20BlackRock%20veteran%20who%20is%20also%20the%20global%20head%20of%20corporate%20strategy%2C%20named%20cultural%20fit%20as%20his%20top%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20acquire%20the%20kind%20of%20people%20that%20are%20aligned%20to%20a%20'One%20BlackRock'%20culture%20and%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20firm's%20ethos%20of%20working%20collaboratively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20was%20part%20of%20many%20meetings%20with%20HPS's%20executive%20team%20to%20test%20the%20waters.%20He%20said%20the%20cofounders%20shared%20important%20values%20with%20Fink%20and%20BlackRock%20President%20Rob%20Kapito.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20speak%20the%20same%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20founders.%20Larry%20Fink%20and%20Rob%20Kapito%20are%20founders.%20We're%20client-centered%20firms.%20We%20believe%20in%20scale%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20global.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20cofounders%20of%20HPS%20%E2%80%94%20Scott%20Kanick%2C%20Mike%20Patterson%2C%20and%20Scot%20French%20%E2%80%94%20will%20lead%20a%20new%20private%20financing%20solutions%20unit%20at%20BlackRock%20and%20join%20the%20firm's%20global%20executive%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a6c590a-fdbf-4fc1-8b90-944e82342226%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnrich%20and%20extend%20BlackRock's%20platform%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlackRock%20only%20makes%20acquisitions%20that%20are%20additive%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20in%20all%20the%20businesses%20that%20we've%20acquired%2C%20whether%20it's%20private%20credit%20or%20infrastructure%20or%20SMA%20or%20options%20or%20whatever.%20We've%20done%20technology%20and%20data%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Small%20said.%