ands%20of%20missing%20detainees%20have%20mobilised%2C%20searching%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%20held%20in%20prisons.%20As%20rebels%20advanced%2C%20they%20released%20many%20prisoners%20but%20many%20more%20remain%20unaccounted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20whoever%20emerges%20in%20power%20must%20hold%20Assad%20and%20his%20associates%20accountable%20for%20their%20crimes.%20Syrian%20rescue%20groups%20are%20calling%20for%20assistance%20in%20locating%20secret%20jails%20and%20detainees%2C%20while%20the%20Israeli%20military%20has%20launched%20several%20airstrikes%20in%20Syria%2C%20targeting%20military%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Damascus%2C%20life%20is%20gradually%20returning%20to%20normal%2C%20but%20the%20scars%20of%20war%20remain.%20Banks%20and%20shops%20reopened%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20traffic%20flowed%20back%20onto%20the%20roads%2C%20and%20street%20cleaners%20were%20busy%20clearing%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20armed%20men%20has%20significantly%20reduced%2C%20with%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20rebels%20confirming%20that%20their%20command%20has%20ordered%20fighters%20to%20withdraw%20from%20urban%20areas.%20In%20their%20place%2C%20police%20and%20internal%20security%20forces%20linked%20to%20the%20rebel%20group%20HTS%20have%20taken%20over%20to%20maintain%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733906520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fplt40fd_mohammad-albashir_625x300_11_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-mohammad-al-bashir-syrias-post-assad-prime-minister-7221254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammad%20al-Bashir%20worked%20for%20Syria's%20state%20gas%20company%20before%20entering%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-mohammad-al-bashir-syrias-post-assad-prime-minister-7221254%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A