ces%20multiple%20charges%20there%20as%20well%20as%20murder%20charges%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20police%20say%20the%20head%20of%20one%20of%20US's%20biggest%20health%20insurers%20was%20deliberately%20targeted%2C%20a%20trail%20of%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20by%20Mangione%20could%20point%20to%20likely%20grievances%20he%20harboured%20against%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20Mangione%20was%20also%20arrested%20with%20a%20manifesto%20where%20he%20accused%20health%20insurance%20companies%20for%20putting%20corporate%20greed%20over%20the%20well-being%20of%20people%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F12%2F10%2Fus-news%2Fluigi-mangiones-back-pain-was-so-intense-that-he-couldnt-be-physically-intimate-with-anyone-former-landlord-says%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENY%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20theories%20that%20the%20murder%20could%20be%20linked%20to%20Mangione's%20disappointment%20with%20the%20insurance%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20lived%20in%20Hawaii%20in%202022%20and%2C%20according%20to%20his%20former%20roommate%20RJ%20Martin%2C%20suffered%20from%20back%20pain%2C%20and%20was%20hoping%20to%20strengthen%20his%20back.%20After%20a%20surfing%20lesson%2C%20Mangione%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20bed%20for%20about%20a%20week%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20pain%2C%20Martin%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Mangione%20confirmed%20he'd%20had%20back%20surgery%20and%20sent%20him%20photos%20of%20the%20X-rays%2C%20Martin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20the%20manager%20of%20Surfbreak%2C%20the%20co-living%20residence%20in%20Hawaii%20he%20resided%20at%2C%20that%20he%20had%20a%20back%20problem%2C%20and%20in%20August%20of%202023%20sent%20him%20pictures%20of%20a%20back%20surgery%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%20%26quot%3BHis%20spine%20was%20kind%20of%20misaligned.%20He%20said%20his%20lower%20vertebrae%20were%20almost%20like%20a%20half-inch%20off%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20pinched%20a%20nerve%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Martin%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F12%2F09%2Fnyregion%2Funited-healthcare-ceo-shooting-luigi-mangione.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20that%20dating%20and%20being%20physically%20intimate%20with%20his%20back%20condition%20wasn't%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20while%20saying%20that%20Mangione%20was%20a%20young%20man%20yearning%20a%20normal%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Martin%20said%20that%20Mangione%20left%20Hawaii%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023%2C%20presumably%20for%20an%20operation%20on%20his%20back.%20In%20August%20that%20year%2C%20he%20checked%20in%20via%20text%20to%20see%20how%20his%20friend%20was%20doing%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20he%20sent%20me%20back%20pictures%20of%20his%20back%20surgery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20X%20profile%2C%20he%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20x-ray%20of%20a%20spinal%20surgery%20and%20on%20GoodReads%2C%20he%20reviewed%20a%20book%20called%20%26quot%3BCrooked%3A%20Outwitting%20the%20Back%20Pain%20Industry%20and%20Getting%20on%20the%20Road%20to%20Recovery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20account%20was%20narrated%20by%20Paul%20Piek%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20software%20testing%20professional%20from%20Flensburg%2C%20Germany%2C%20met%20Mangione%20in%20March%20while%20watching%20a%20muay%20thai%20boxing%20fight%20in%20Ao%20Nang%2C%20Thailand.%20The%20two%20and%20another%20friend%20of%20Piek's%20met%20up%20again%20in%20Krabi%2C%20Thailand%20on%20April%208%20and%20roadtripped%20through%20Khao%20Sok%20and%20Bangkok%2C%20where%20they%20shared%20a%20hotel%20room%20for%20four%20nights%20and%20visited%20temples.%20%26quot%3BHe%20told%20us%20he%20did%20(muy%20thai)%20before%20his%20injury%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Piek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiek%20said%20Mangione%20told%20him%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20hiking%20when%20they%20met%2C%20with%20no%20further%20mention%20of%20his%20back%20injury.%20%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20seem%20like%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20he%20did%20opt%20out%20of%20one%20guided%20hike%20for%20an%20easier%20walk%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20had%20left%20his%20previous%20employer%20Truecar%2C%20a%20car-purchse%20platform%20with%20offices%20in%20California%2C%20in%202023%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20A%20colleague%20he%20worked%20with%20there%20told%20Reuters%20he%20took%20leave%20during%20the%20middle%20of%202023%20for%20about%20two%20months%2C%20a%20move%20the%20colleague's%20manager%20told%20him%20was%20due%20to%20back-related%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20a%20deleted%20Reddit%20account%20allegedly%20associated%20with%20Mangione%20wrote%20multiple%20comments%20in%20a%20subreddit%20for%20people%20diagnosed%20with%20spondylolisthesis%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftylerroush%2F2024%2F12%2F10%2Funitedhealthcare-shooting-suspect-luigi-mangione-appeared-to-suffer-from-rare-back-condition-heres-what-to-know%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reported.%20The%20user%20wrote%20the%20condition%20%26quot%3Bwent%20bad%20on%20me%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20devastating%20as%20a%20young%20athletic%20person%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20learned%20the%20condition%20would%20force%20them%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20desk%20job%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2014-page%20handwritten%20document%20that%20Sky%20News%20identified%20as%20having%20been%20uploaded%20to%20his%20Google%20Drive%20account%20in%202021%20and%20which%20has%20not%20been%20independently%20verified%20by%20Reuters%2C%20Mangione%20said%20he%20had%20a%20back%20injury%20known%20as%20an%20L5-S1%20isthmic%20spondylolisthesis%2C%20in%20which%20one%20of%20the%20bones%20in%20the%20spine%20slips%20forward%20and%20presses%20on%20the%20vertebra%20below%20it.%20Mangione's%20notes%20mention%20that%20his%20condition%20involved%20a%20stress%20fracture%20in%20the%20pars%20bone%20that%20connects%20the%20vertebrae%20to%20the%20spinal%20column.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione's%20profile%20on%20X%20includes%20an%20X-ray%20of%20a%20person%20who%20has%20had%20an%20L5-S1%20spinal%20operation%20in%20which%20two%20vertebra%20are%20surgically%20fused%20together.%20The%20surgery%20has%20an%20overall%20success%20rate%20of%2080%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733904720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ff75gmjpg_luigi-mangione-xray_625x300_11_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-luigi-mangione-killed-unitedhealthcare-ceo-a-chronic-back-pain-link-7221725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chronic%20back%20pain%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20point%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20murder%20investigation%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%2C%20who%2026-year-old%20Luigi%20Mangione%20gunned%20down%20in%20New%20York%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-luigi-mangione-killed-unitedhealthcare-ceo-a-chronic-back-pain-link-7221725%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20jawans%20injured%2C%20one%20Maoist%20killed%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20encounter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733904558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116205689%2Cimgsize-1758103.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftwo-jawans-injured-one-maoist-killed-in-chhattisgarh-encounter%2Farticleshow%2F116204561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20District%20Reserve%20Guards%20(DRG)%20personnel%20were%20injured%20in%20an%20IED%20blast%20during%20a%20clash%20with%20Maoists%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bijapur%20district%20on%20Wednesday.%20One%20Maoist%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%2