hom%20Brussels%2C%20and%20now%20Washington%2C%20can%20do%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fgiorgia-meloni-named-the-most-powerful-person-in-europe%2Farticleshow%2F116200014.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fgiorgia-meloni-named-the-most-powerful-person-in-europe%2Famp_articleshow%2F116200014.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fgiorgia-meloni-named-the-most-powerful-person-in-europe%2Famp_articleshow%2F116200014.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Atul%20Subhash%20Suicide%20Shocker%2C%20Supreme%20Court's%20Big%20Remark%20On%20Dowry%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFlagging%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20tendency%20to%20misuse%26quot%3B%20laws%20protecting%20women%20from%20cruelty%20by%20their%20in-laws%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20courts%20must%20exercise%20caution%20while%20deciding%20dowry%20harassment%20cases%20to%20prevent%20unnecessary%20harassment%20of%20innocent%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20are%20significant%20amid%20a%20nationwide%20debate%20on%20the%20misuse%20of%20dowry%20prohibition%20laws%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%2034-year-old%20man's%20suicide%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Before%20he%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20recorded%20an%2080-minute%20video%20in%20which%20he%20accused%20his%20estranged%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%20and%20her%20family%20of%20slapping%20multiple%20cases%20on%20him%20and%20his%20family%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20them.%20Atul%20Subhash%20also%20criticised%20the%20justice%20system%20in%20his%2024-page%20suicide%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20tough%20remarks%20came%20as%20it%20set%20aside%20a%20Telangana%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20had%20refused%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20dowry%20harassment%20case%20against%20a%20man%2C%20his%20parents%20and%20other%20family%20members.%20The%20court%20said%20an%20examination%20of%20the%20FIR%20shows%20that%20the%20wife's%20allegations%20were%20%26quot%3Bvague%20and%20omnibus%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20some%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20no%20connection%20to%20the%20matter%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20dragged%20into%20the%20web%20of%20crime%20without%20any%20rhyme%20or%20reason%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mere%20reference%20to%20the%20names%20of%20family%20members%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20arising%20out%20of%20a%20matrimonial%20dispute%2C%20without%20specific%20allegations%20indicating%20their%20active%20involvement%20should%20be%20nipped%20in%20the%20bud%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20well-recognised%20fact%2C%20borne%20out%20of%20judicial%20experience%2C%20that%20there%20is%20often%20a%20tendency%20to%20implicate%20all%20the%20members%20of%20the%20husband's%20family%20when%20domestic%20disputes%20arise%20out%20of%20a%20matrimonial%20discord%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20such%20sweeping%20accusations%20unsupported%20by%20concrete%20evidence%20cannot%20form%20the%20basis%20for%20prosecution%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%20said%20in%20its%20order%2C%20%26quot%3BCourts%20must%20exercise%20caution%20in%20such%20cases%20to%20prevent%20misuse%20of%20legal%20provisions%20and%20the%20legal%20process%20and%20avoid%20unnecessary%20harassment%20of%20innocent%20family%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20which%20punishes%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20by%20her%20husband%20or%20his%20relatives%2C%20was%20incorporated%20into%20a%20law%20to%20ensure%20swift%20intervention%20by%20the%20State.%20With%20IPC%20replaced%20by%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Section%2080%20now%20deals%20with%20dowry%20death%20and%20Section%2085%20with%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20by%20her%20husband%20or%20his%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20notable%20rise%20in%20matrimonial%20disputes%20across%20the%20country%2C%20accompanied%20by%20growing%20discord%20and%20tension%20within%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage.%20%26quot%3B...consequently%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20tendency%20to%20misuse%20provisions%20like%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20IPC%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20unleashing%20personal%20vendetta%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20by%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20vague%20and%20generalised%20allegations%20during%20matrimonial%20conflicts%2C%20if%20not%20scrutinized%2C%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20misuse%20of%20legal%20processes%20and%20an%20encouragement%20for%20use%20of%20arm%20twisting%20tactics%20by%20a%20wife%20and%2For%20her%20family.%20Sometimes%2C%20recourse%20is%20taken%20to%20invoke%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20IPC%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20in%20order%20to%20seek%20compliance%20with%20the%20unreasonable%20demands%20of%20a%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20clarified%20that%20it%20was%20not%20stating%20that%20any%20woman%20who%20has%20suffered%20cruelty%20should%20remain%20silent.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20the%20intention%20of%20our%20aforesaid%20observations%20but%20we%20should%20not%20encourage%20a%20case%20like%20as%20in%20the%20present%20one%2C%20where%20as%20a%20counterblast%20to%20the%20petition%20for%20dissolution%20of%20marriage%20sought%20by%20the%20first%20appellant-husband%20of%20the%20second%20respondent%20herein%2C%20a%20complaint%20under%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20IPC%20is%20lodged%20by%20the%20latter.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20insertion%20of%20the%20said%20provision%20is%20meant%20mainly%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20subjected%20to%20cruelty%20in%20the%20matrimonial%20home%20primarily%20due%20to%20an%20unlawful%20demand%20for%20any%20property%20or%20valuable%20security%20in%20the%20form%20of%20dowry.%20However%2C%20sometimes%20it%20is%20misused%20as%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20he%20shot%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20said%20he%20married%20in%202019%20after%20finding%20Nikita%20Singhania%20on%20a%20matchmaking%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20Nikita%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20under%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20unnatural%20sex.%20She%20alleged%20that%20he%20demanded%20a%20dowry%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20this%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20father%20and%20he%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20some%20poor%20bollywood%20plot.%20She%20has%20already%20confessed%20that%20her%20father%20was%20suffering%20from%20long%20term%20illness%20in%20her%20cross%20examination.%20Her%20father%20was%20getting%20treated%20from%20AIIMS%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20for%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%20etc.%20Doctors%20gave%20him%20few%20months%20and%20hence%20we%20got%20married%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20This%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20subsequently%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20accused%20his%20wife%20of%20filing%20false%20cases%20against%20his%20elderly%20parents%20and%20brother%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20assaulting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaging%20against%20the%20law%20dealing%20with%20such%20cases%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%2