%20Pennsylvania%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuigi's%20family%20history%20is%20one%20of%20immigrant%20success.%20His%20late%20grandfather%2C%20Nick%20Mangione%20Sr%2C%20often%20shared%20his%20rags-to-riches%20story%2C%20proudly%20recounting%20his%20rise%20from%20humble%20beginnings.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20have%20two%20nickels%20to%20rub%20together%20when%20my%20father%20died%20when%20I%20was%2011%2C%20yet%20I%20still%20became%20a%20millionaire%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20had%20said%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebaltimorebanner.com%2Fcommunity%2Fcriminal-justice%2Fluigi-mangione-family-baltimore-towson-GPRMNCATXRGDJAUZXJQO6RHSHU%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Baltimore%20Sun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recalling%20his%20father's%20struggles%20as%20an%20Italian%20immigrant%20and%20his%20own%20determination.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20other%20country%20can%20you%20do%20that%20in%3F%20None%20that%20I%20can%20think%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENick%20Mangione's%20empire%20spanned%20a%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20from%20owning%20local%20resorts%20and%20country%20clubs%20to%20operating%20nursing%20homes%20and%20even%20a%20radio%20station.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Mary%2C%20were%20also%20philanthropists%2C%20donating%20millions%2C%20including%20over%20%241%20million%20to%20the%20Greater%20Baltimore%20Medical%20Centre%2C%20where%20all%20of%20their%2037%20grandchildren%20were%20born.%20In%20honour%20of%20their%20contributions%2C%20the%20hospital%20even%20named%20its%20obstetrics%20unit%20after%20the%20Mangione%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mangione%20Family%20Foundation%20has%20also%20made%20significant%20donations%20to%20institutions%20like%20St.%20Jude%20Children's%20Research%20Hospital%20and%20St.%20Joseph%20Medical%20Centre%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland.%20Loyola%20University's%20pools%20are%20named%20after%20them%2C%20and%20several%20family%20members%2C%20including%20six%20of%20Nick%20a