.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMichele%20Morrone's%20representative%20denied%20affair%20rumors%20with%20Megan%20Fox%2C%20clarifying%20their%20relationship%20as%20strictly%20professional.%20A%20resurfaced%20video%20from%20the%20set%20of%20their%20film%20'Subservience'%20fueled%20speculation%20amidst%20Fox's%20reported%20split%20from%20Machine%20Gun%20Kelly.%20Morrone%20is%20currently%20filming%20in%20Italy%2C%20while%20Fox%20is%20pregnant%20and%20expecting%20her%20fourth%20child%20in%20March%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fmichele-morrone-reacts-to-affair-rumours-with-pregnant-megan-fox-amidst-her-split-from-machine-gun-kelly%2Farticleshow%2F116197590.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBengaluru%20To%20Jaunpur%2040%20Times%26quot%3B%3A%20Atul%20Subhash's%20Family%20On%20What%20He%20Suffered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%2034-year-old%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20alleging%20extortion%20and%20harassment%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%20and%20her%20family%2C%20have%20said%20he%20was%20under%20severe%20stress%20and%20had%20to%20travel%20at%20least%2040%20times%20between%20Bengaluru%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jaunpur%20for%20court%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tortured%20my%20son%2C%20they%20tortured%20us%20too.%20But%20my%20son%20took%20everything%20upon%20himself.%20He%20endured%20everything%2C%20he%20did%20not%20let%20us%20suffer.%20He%20kept%20burning%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Atul's%20mother%2C%20crushed%20by%20her%20son's%20death.%C2%A0His%20father%20said%20Atul%20had%20told%20them%20the%20family%20court%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%20the%20judge%20and%20others%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20law%2C%20did%20not%20even%20follow%20the%20guidelines%20of%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20must%20have%20travelled%20between%20Bengaluru%20and%20Jaunpur%20at%20least%2040%20times.%20So%20many%20charges%2C%20one%20case%20would%20finish%20and%20she%20(the%20wife)%20would%20slap%20another.%20He%20was%20frustrated%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20show%20it%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20Bengaluru%20home%20on%20Monday%20morning.%20A%20'justice%20is%20due'%20placard%20and%20a%2024-page%20suicide%20note%20was%20found%20in%20his%20room.%20He%20has%20accused%20his%20estranged%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20mother-in-law%20Nisha%20Singhania%2C%20brother-in-law%20Anurag%20Singhania%20and%20his%20wife's%20uncle%20Sushil%20Singhania%20of%20instigating%20him%20to%20die%20by%20suicide.%20Based%20on%20his%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar's%20complaint%2C%20a%20case%20of%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideos%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fid%3D871784%26mute%3D1%26autostart%3D1%26mutestart%3Dtrue%26pWidth%3D100%26pHeight%3D100%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%2081-minute%20video%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20said%20he%20married%20in%202019%20after%20finding%20Nikita%20on%20a%20matchmaking%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20she%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20under%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20unnatural%20sex.%20She%20alleged%20that%20he%20demanded%20dowry%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20this%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20father%20and%20he%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20some%20poor%20bollywood%20plot.%20She%20has%20already%20confessed%20that%20her%20father%20was%20suffering%20from%20long%20term%20illness%20in%20her%20cross%20examination.%20Her%20father%20was%20getting%20treated%20from%20AIIMS%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20for%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%20etc.%20Doctors%20gave%20him%20few%20months%20and%20hence%20we%20got%20married%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20This%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20subsequently%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20first%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case%2C%20but%20later%20hiked%20this%20to%20Rs%203%20crore.%20He%20has%20detailed%20a%20court%20exchange%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20when%20he%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20men%20are%20dying%20by%20suicide%20due%20to%20false%20cases%2C%20his%20wife%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20why%20don't%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20judge%20laughed%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20room.%20Atul%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bmust%20think%20about%20his%20family%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20%26quot%3Bsettle%20the%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul's%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BAround%20eight%20months%20after%20my%20brother's%20wife%20separated%20from%20him%2C%20she%20filed%20a%20divorce%20case%20and%20framed%20many%20charges%20against%20my%20brother%20and%20our%20entire%20family%20under%20different%20acts%20and%20sections.%20Every%20law%20in%20India%20is%20for%20women%2C%20and%20not%20for%20men%20-%20my%20brother%20fought%20for%20this%20but%20he%20left%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20did%20everything%20for%20her.%20Whatever%20has%20happened%20was%20unfortunate.%20If%20he%20had%20ever%20discussed%20it%20with%20me%20or%20our%20father%2C%20we%20would%20have%20helped%20him%20out%20of%20this%20situation...%20I%20want%20to%20request%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20President%20that%20justice%20must%20be%20done%20to%20my%20brother%20if%20he%20is%20right.%20Otherwise%2C%20show%20me%20the%20proof%20that%20he%20is%20wrong.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20proper%20investigation%20against%20the%20judge%20named%20in%20my%20brother's%20suicide%20note%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Santosh%20friend%20Jackson%20told%20ANI%20that%20he%20was%20under%20tremendous%20stress.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20this%20particular%20video%20and%20the%20notes%20that%20he%20has%20made%2C%20it%20doesn't%20seem%20that%20he%20was%20depressed.%20It%20seems%20that%20he%20did%20it%20out%20of%20a%20sense%20of%20harassment%20that%20he%20was%20facing%20from%20the%20system.%20So%20it%20was%20more%20like%20his%20way%20of%20telling%20the%20system%20that%20it%20is%20not%20helping%20men%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20bias.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaging%20against%20the%20law%20dealing%20with%20such%20cases%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20work%20hard%20and%20become%20better%20at%20my%20work%2C%20the%20more%20I%20and%20my%20family%20will%20be%20harassed%20and%20extorted%20and%20the%20whole%20legal%20system%20will%20encourage%20and%20help%20my%20harassers...%20Now%2C%20with%20me%20gone%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20money%20and%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20reason%20to%20harass%20my%20old%20parents%20and%20my%20brother.%20I%20may%20have%20destroyed%20my%20body%20but%20it%20has%20saved%20everything%20I%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJackson%20said%20the%20couple's%20relationship%20went%20downhill%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20COVID%2C%20he%20was%20looking%20after%20his%20wife%20and%20son.%20His%20wife%20was%20also%20infected%20with%20COVID%