r-syrias-caretaker-prime-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F116198755.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Techie%20Suicide%3A%20FIR%20Against%20Atul%20Subhash's%20Wife%2C%20In-Laws%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20Bengaluru%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20alleging%20harassment%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%20in%20videos%20and%20posts%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20his%20wife%2C%20her%20family%20members%2C%20and%20a%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBikas%20Kumar%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatul-subhash-nikita-singhania-bengaluru-to-jaunpur-40-times-atul-subhashs-family-on-what-he-suffered-7221712%5C%22%3Ebrother%20of%20the%2034-year-old%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20filed%20an%20FIR%20(First%20Information%20Report)%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20against%20his%20wife%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20her%20mother%20Nisha%20Singhania%2C%20her%20brother%20Anurag%20Singhania%20and%20her%20uncle%20Sushil%20Singhania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%2C%20who%20was%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20but%20lived%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20worked%20for%20a%20private%20firm%2C%20left%20a%2024-page%20note%20detailing%20what%20he%20alleged%20was%20years%20of%20emotional%20distress%20because%20of%20harassment%20and%20multiple%20cases%20filed%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%2C%20and%20a%20judge%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20details%20emerge%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatul-subhash-dowry-harassment-suicide-bengaluru-suicide-have-bath-finish-office-tasks-bengaluru-mans-checklist-before-suicide-7218060%5C%22%3EAtul%20Subhash's%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20videos%2C%20the%20family%20is%20in%20shock%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20seek%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20did%20everything%20for%20her.%20Whatever%20has%20happened%20was%20unfortunate.%20If%20he%20had%20ever%20discussed%20it%20with%2