2C%20and%20executive%20groups.%20In%20the%20US%20commercial%20group%2C%20Gemini%20scored%20lower%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-artificial-intelligence-bet-doubts-marc-benioff-satya-nadella-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ChatGPT%20across%20four%20categories%3A%20familiarity%2C%20consideration%2C%20usage%2C%20and%20paid%20usage%2C%20one%20slide%20showed.%20Paid%20usage%20was%20measured%20at%2022%25%2C%2016%20points%20lower%20than%20Copilot%20and%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20for%20the%20UK%20in%20the%20commercial%20group%20also%20showed%20Gemini%20mostly%20behind%20its%20rivals%2C%20although%20it%20scored%20slightly%20higher%20than%20Copilot%20in%20paid%20usage.%20In%20Brazil%20and%20India%2C%20Gemini%20for%20Workspace%20fared%20better%20than%20Copilot%20across%20most%20categories%20but%20still%20fell%20below%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGemini%20trails%20both%20Copilot%20and%20ChatGPT%20in%20established%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Brises%20above%20Copilot%20across%20the%20funnel%26quot%3B%20in%20Brazil%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20part%20of%20Google's%20internal%20presentation%20that%20focused%20on%20brand%20familiarity%2C%20Google's%20Gemini%20for%20Workspace%20came%20in%20last%20place%20in%20consumer%2C%20commercial%2C%20and%20executive%20categories%2C%20trailing%20ChatGPT%2C%20Copilot%2C%20Meta%20AI%2C%20and%20Apple%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamiliarity%20was%20particularly%20low%20for%20the%20US%20consumer%20category%2C%20with%20Gemini%20for%20Workspace%20scoring%20just%2045%25%2C%20while%20Copilot%20scored%2049%25%2C%20ChatGPT%20and%20Apple%20both%20scored%2080%25%2C%20and%20Meta%20scored%2082%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1e5b21f-94ee-4505-b53d-a15001e3e262%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20have%20the%20same%20problem%20as%20Microsoft'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3